    "narrative": "The Ghost Ride the WHIP lineup is anchored by **Vinnie Pasquantino** (76.21) and **Mickey Moniak** (73.15), who represent our most efficient opportunities for production today. **Vinnie Pasquantino** benefits significantly from a favorable dynamic platoon split against Bibee, while **Mickey Moniak** is positioned in the leadoff spot against a vulnerable pitcher, with the park factors and wind providing a distinct tailwind for his scoring potential. Similarly, **Seiya Suzuki** (71.23) projects as a premier play; despite a negative platoon adjustment, the matchup against the struggling Petty allows his base projection to soar, making him a cornerstone of today's offensive strategy.\n\nEfficiency remains the priority as we navigate the scarcity of stolen bases. While **Jose Caballero** (47.55) projects lower than our core, his ability to manipulate the basepaths against the slow delivery of Baz remains a calculated gamble we are willing to take, even with his suboptimal spot at the bottom of the order. Our most difficult decision arrived at the utility position, where **Cole Young** (48.11) was narrowly edged out by the high-floor profile of **Josh Naylor** (70.82). While **Cole Young** showed promise, **Josh Naylor**\u2019s elite matchup against Ritchie combined with his strong protection in the #3 hole made him the clear optimizer choice to maximize run production.\n\nWe must remain vigilant regarding the 34% rain risk looming over **Mickey Moniak** and **Kyle Karros**. **Kyle Karros** (45.92) is already functioning at our absolute floor, with his score depressed by a challenging matchup against Brazob\u00e1n and negative park effects; any weather-related delays could effectively render his game a wash. Conversely, we are keeping **Austin Riley** (42.82) on the bench today as he faces the elite arm of Gilbert; his matchup against a high-caliber starter provides a significantly lower efficiency ceiling than our active lineup, keeping him on the sidelines to preserve our limited game caps for more favorable situations.",
